#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.25"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.25:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Ayoguḷavagga"
msgstr "3. The Iron Ball"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Paṭhamaphalasutta"
msgstr "25. Fruits (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.285"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.25:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, iddhipādā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four bases of psychic power."

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ "
"iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.4"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "energy …"

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.5"
msgid "cittasamādhi …"
msgstr "mental development …"

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.6"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti—"
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.7"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro iddhipādā."
msgstr "These are the four bases of psychic power."

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.8"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"bhikkhunā dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Because of developing and cultivating these four bases of psychic power, one "
"of two results can be expected:"

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.9"
msgid "diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā”ti."
msgstr ""
"enlightenment in the present life, or if there’s something left over, non-"
"return.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.25:1.10"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
